<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Coral Springs</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Located on the eastern edge of the city, Coral Springs is a charming residential neighborhood of North East Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">One of the most recently developed communities Coral Springs was established in 1991 and is surrounded by a number of Streets and Boulevards in all directions.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The architectural style and layout of the community in Coral Springs is heavily inspired by the Californian Theme, with a massive 16-acre lake situated right in the heart of the neighborhood.</p>

